<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4631813>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 14. Left parapodia of a non-type epitokous female of Nectoneanthes uchiwa sp. nov. (NSMT-Pol 11409) collected from the mouth of Omuta-gawa River, Ariake Sea. (A) Anterior view of parapodium 2; (B) posterior view of parapodium 14; (C) posterior view of parapodium 57; (D) posterior view of parapodium 96. Abbreviations same as for those in Figures 11 and 13. Arrows indicate an ovoid lobe above the dorsal cirrus. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4631813/files/figure.png" .

