<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4631803>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 11. Anterior views of parapodia of the holotype of Nectoneanthes uchiwa sp. nov. (NSMT Pol H-549). (A) Parapodium 2 (right); (B) parapodium 13 (left); (C) parapodium 65 (left); (D) parapodium 125 (right). no, notoacicula; ne, neuroacicula; dc, dorsal cirrus; nod, notopodial dorsal ligule; nop, notopodial prechaetal lobe; nov, notopodial ventral ligule; nep, neuropodial postchaetal lobe; nei, neuropodial inferior lobe; nev, neuropodial ventral ligule; vc, ventral cirrus. Arrows indicate an ovoid lobe above the dorsal cirrus. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4631803/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4631809>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 13. Anterior views of right parapodia of a non-type epitokous male of Nectoneanthes uchiwa sp. nov. (NSMT-Pol 11410) collected from the mouth of Omuta-gawa River, Ariake Sea. (A) Parapodium 2; (B) parapodium 15; (C) parapodium 47; (D) parapodium 93. au, additional lobe at upper portion on base of ventral cirrus; al, additional lobe at lower portion on base of ventral cirrus; z, protozoan colony. The other abbreviations same as those in Figure 11. Arrows indicate an ovoid lobe above the dorsal cirrus. Scale bar, 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4631809/files/figure.png" .

