<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4631805>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 12. Chaetae of Nectoneanthes uchiwa sp. nov. (A–C) Holotype at atokous stage (NSMT Pol H-549): (A) sesquigomph spiniger from notopodium in chaetiger 13; (B) sesquigomph spiniger from neuropodium in chaetiger 13; (C) heterogomph spiniger from neuropodium in chaetiger 12. (D) Non-type epitokous male (NSMT-Pol 11410) collected from the mouth of Omuta-gawa River, Ariake Sea, epitokous natatory chaeta from modified notopodium in chaetiger 46. (E) Non-type juvenile (1.1 mm BW, NSMT-Pol 11411) collected from Beolkyo Bay, Korea, juvenile-specific heterogomph falciger from neuropodium in chaetiger 9. Scale bar, 0.1 mm for A–D, 0.05 mm for E." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4631805/files/figure.png" .

